data.title: HUGE SIEGE BATTLE - Third Age Total War Gameplay
data.description:
Third Age Total War Gameplay - It is the Second Age, The Dark Lord sets his eyes upon Rhun. after having subdued the Nazgul, Khamul the Easterling to Saurons will, Khamul was sent on his first great quest to conquer and recruit the Easterlings to Saurons Will. On this occasion Kahmul and his legions ran into an unforeseen circumstance.
A bordering fortress from the Kingdom of Arnor stood in its path to the Rhunic Borderlands. Thinking it is an easy target for slaughter, Khamuls is set upon this Fortress, for it has potential to act as a Headquarters to his Easterlings campaign. However Rhun has decided to strike at both Mordor and Arnor while the chaos ensues, they will not sit back and wait for their doom.

Rules-
Mordor and Rhun compete to try and conquer Arnors Castle first.
whoever captures Arnors city, they win
Arnor must hold their city.
Arnor must prevent either enemy from killing each others Chief Commanders.
if Rhun kills Kahmul, they win
if Mordor kills Rhuns Chief Commander Ulfang, they win

Battle Download:  I still need to upload the battle.  Check back later today.

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D

data.title: BATTLE OF BYWATER - Third Age Total War Gameplay
data.description:
